context:
KR:
&lt;이상, 이제 각자 방으로 돌아갈 시간이니까…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Yi Sang, the day's over. You can go back to your room now...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그러게, 방에서 좀 있으라니까.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Seriously, I told you that you could rest in your room if you wanted.&gt;

KR:
&lt;당신만큼 고충을 느끼는 사람도 없는데…&gt;
EN:
&lt;You're the one with the biggest share of suffering right now...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래, 들어가.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Yeah, rest well.&gt;

KR:
&lt;아직은… 더 새롭게 생긴 문은 없네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;No new doors... yet.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;...!&gt;

KR:
&lt;으, 응.&gt;
EN:
&lt;O-okay.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…새로운 공간이 생긴 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Is that a new room?&gt;

KR:
&lt;그건 그렇지…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Right, right...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그건 내 뒤에 있던 수감자들도 전부 놀랐었어…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Come on, I wasn't the only one that freaked out. Everyone did...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…꽝인가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;This wasn't it, then?&gt;

KR:
&lt;벌써 새로운 문이 생기기에는 이상할 정도로 빠른… 묘한 시점이라고 생각하긴 했어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Right... I thought it was an awkward time for a new door to appear. Too soon, too soon.&gt;

KR:
&lt;히스클리프도 두 번이나 그러진 않을 거야… 아마.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Even Heathcliff won't do anything like that again. ... Probably.&gt;
